{"text_id":221442,"tokens":["This"," paper"," addresses"," the"," problem"," of"," sentiment"," analysis"," and"," sarcasm"," detection"," in"," user","-","generated"," short"," text"," and"," sentences","."," It"," proposes"," to"," augment"," traditional"," features"," used"," for"," sentiment"," analysis"," and"," sarcasm"," detection"," with"," cognitive"," features"," derived"," from"," the"," eye","-","movement"," patterns"," of"," readers",".","\n","The"," paper","'","s"," strengths"," include"," the"," fact"," that"," it"," provides"," a"," novel"," approach"," to"," sentiment"," analysis"," and"," sarcasm"," detection","."," It"," also"," provides"," statistical"," evidence"," to"," show"," that"," its"," proposed"," approach"," improves"," the"," performance"," of"," polarity"," detection"," by"," a"," maximum"," of"," ","3",".","7","%"," and"," ","9",".","3","%"," on"," two"," datasets","."," Additionally",","," the"," paper"," provides"," evidence"," through"," feature"," significance"," analysis"," and"," an"," experiment"," on"," a"," held","-","out"," dataset"," that"," cognitive"," features"," indeed"," empower"," sentiment"," analy","zers"," to"," handle"," complex"," constructs",".","\n","The"," paper","'","s"," weaknesses"," include"," the"," fact"," that"," it"," does"," not"," provide"," a"," comprehensive"," evaluation"," of"," its"," proposed"," approach","."," Additionally",","," the"," paper"," does"," not"," provide"," a"," comparison"," with"," existing"," approaches",","," which"," would"," be"," beneficial"," for"," understanding"," the"," impact"," of"," the"," proposed"," approach","."," Finally",","," the"," paper"," does"," not"," provide"," a"," detailed"," discussion"," of"," the"," implications"," of"," its"," findings","."],"sub_source":"peerread","model":"davinci","label":1}